race.comment: PERFECT RULER (1) hits this third-up and ready to peak, stepping out to the mile now where he's performed very strongly in the past. He maps beautifully and the claim of Tsang comes in handy. Likely to be on the speed from the outset and he'll be hard to reel in. MIDSUMMER ROMANCE (8) should appreciate getting out to the mile now third-up into the campaign after flashing late last time out over 1400m. She's likely to be back from the draw once again, but she'll be rattling home late in the piece. REIGN IN THE CASH (2) is another who looks better suited getting out to the mile now. He's raced well over 1500m in SA earlier this campaign and Page is having some success bringing these horses across the border. Nicely drawn and can be in the finish. SHE'SATROOPER (6) looks as though she'll appreciate the rise in trip and can put her best foot forward again. WRITTEN SIN (7) is next best.
